name: Apple 2021 11-inch iPad Pro (Wi-Fi, 1TB) - Silver with AppleCare+ (2 Years)
feature_bullets: Apple M1 chip for next-level performance,Stunning 11-inch Liquid Retina display with ProMotion, True Tone, and P3 wide color,TrueDepth camera system featuring Ultra Wide front camera with Center Stage,AppleCare+ for iPad extends your repair coverage and technical support to two years from your AppleCare+ purchase date,It adds coverage for up to two incidents of accidental damage protection every 12 months, each subject to a service fee of $49 for your iPad and $29 for Apple Pencil or Apple- branded iPad keyboard, plus applicable tax,Get 24/7 priority access to Apple experts by chat or phone

name: iPad 9th/8th/7th Generation Keyboard Case 10.2 inch 2021/2020/2019, iPad Pro 10.5-inch Case with Keyboard,iPad Air 3 2019, 7 Color Backlit Removable Bluetooth Wireless Keyboard Folio Case(Purple)
feature_bullets: ??IPad 10.2/10.5 inch Keyboard Case Compatibility???No pen or charger included!??The iPad keyboard case is designed for new iPad 9th 2021 (Model number: A2602/A2603/ A2604/ A2605),8th 2020 released (A2430/A2270/ A2428/ A2429), iPad 7th Generation 10.2 inch 2019 released (A2197/A2198/A2200), iPad Air 3 10.5" 2019 released (A2152/A2123/A2153/A2154) and iPad Pro 10.5 inch 2017 released (A1701/A1709/A1852). Please check the back bottom of your iPad to find the model number.,??Colorful Backlit Keyboard & Hybrid Shockproof Protective Cover?Optional backlight mode and 7 vibrant colors make typing fun and easy in the dark. Scissors mechanical keyboard feels quiet and smooth. The protective case inner layer is of honeycomb grid pattern cushion that releases more 80% hotness than other iPad cases, prevent overheating to extend your iPad life and maximizing screen protection.,??Multiple Viewing Angles & Removeable Magnetic Keyboard?The flip leather case intends to combine tablet and keyboard which form a laptop with keyboard function to work easier. The smart folio keyboard and magnetic case allow us to adjust screen vision and typing position. Secure magentic closure enables you to take the tablet keyboard and a hard shell with you. In case you don't need the Bluetooth keyboard for your iPad sometimes, remove the keyboard and wear the iPad case.,??Bulit-in Rechargeable Keyboard & Auto Sleep/Wake Magnetic Case?The keyboard USB charge cables are attached with the parcel. After 2-3 hours of full charge, the wireless keyboard stands by for 90 days. The smart cover puts your iPad sleep automatically when shut. ?: To reach the best effection of sleep/wake-up, please take the keyboard off; cause the keyboard with iron may hinder the mutual attraction among the magnets.,?? 10.2/10.5 inch iPad Pencil Holder & Warranty Support?Built-in Pencil holder(for iPad) leave a slot to settle your Stylus Pen and had a photo window. Port covers keep dust out. Waterproof, durable, anti-scratch lining, reliable fit your iPad 10.2/10.5 tablet. We provides our customers with a 24/7 Email Service & 30-day Returnable Guarantee. Please feel free to contact us.

feature_bullets: TOUCHPAD FUNCTIONALITY - With upgraded built-in touchpad makes your iPad like a laptop, fast and smooth! Special for iPad Pro 12.9 inch 6th Generation 2022(A2436/A2764/A2437/A2766); iPad Pro 12.9 inch 5th Generation 2021 (A2378/A2379/A2461/A2462), iPad Pro 12.9 inch 4th Generation 2020 (A2229/A2069/A2232/A2233), iPad Pro 12.9 inch 3rd Generation 2018 (A1876/A2014/A1895/A1983). Make sure your iPad iOS system up to 13.2.2 or above & iPad Assistive Touch toggle function on.,RAINBOW BACKLITS - Backlit iPad keyboard case ensures you dont have any trouble while typing in low-lit environment. The keyboard lights up with different colors and can be turned up brighter or dimmer as needed. The battery of touch iPad keyboard supports you to work up to 150 hours when the backlit off and 3 hours when backlit on.,MULTIPLE VIEWING ANGLES - With 360 swivel & 180 flip case, your iPad screen will have multiple viewing angles. You can display your work presentation, watch your favorite show or read a new book. Its also a great helper for your kids to do their homework. There is no limits to places, you can take it out for a vacation, on your bed, on your table.,AUTO WAKE & SLEEP - Trackpad iPad keyboard can automatically enter into sleep mode once close it to save energy and extend standby time. The keyboard case is a durable hard case with all the cut outs in the right places for getting to ports and controls, also offers your iPad full protection to keep your iPad free from scratches, dust, wear and tear.,BUY WITH CONFIDENCE - Free replacement is offered within 1 year by our keyboard. We provide unlimited customer service support and tech support. Questions will be responded to within 12 working hours. It is a must have for anyone with iPad Pro 12.9-inch 3rd/4th/5th Generation.

name: Logitech Combo Touch iPad Air Keyboard Case, Detachable Backlit Keyboard with Kickstand, Trackpad, Smart Connector, Oxford Gray, USA Layout
feature_bullets: Compatible with iPad Air (4th and 5th generation - 2020, 2022) - A2316, A2324, A2325, A2072.Viewing Angles: 10°-60°,Do it all with Combo Touch: Four versatile use modes allow you to type, sketch, view and read without ever having to remove your iPad Air from the keyboard case,Detachable keyboard and adjustable kickstand: Remove the keyboard when you're done typing for more flexibility and enjoy 50 degrees of adjustable viewing angles,Large, click-anywhere trackpad: This iPad keyboard case features a responsive and reliable trackpad that allows you to use the entire surface to work and perform Multi-Touch trackpad gestures,Backlit, laptop-like keyboard: Backlit keys auto-adjust to your environment with 16 levels of brightness and a full row of iPadOS shortcut keys provide one-tap access to volume controls and more,Front, back and corner protection: A durable form-fit cover protects the front, back, and corners of your iPad Air, securely holding it in place no matter what youre doing,SMART CONNECTOR technology: Enjoy instant power and pairing with Combo Touch keyboard case and never worry about charging as power is sourced directly from your iPad Air,Home for Apple Pencil: Easily charge your Apple Pencil while keeping the case on thanks to a convenient opening in the side of the iPad Air case

name: GreenLaw Floating iPad 10th Generation Case with Keyboard, Magnetic Stand, Stain-Resistant Case, 7 Color Backlit, Smart Touchpad Keyboard Case for iPad 10th Gen. 2022, White
feature_bullets: ?? Universal Compatibility: Tailored specifically for the iPad 10th Generation 2022, 10.9-inch (Model: A2696/A2777/A2757). Ensure a perfect fit by checking your iPad's model on the back before purchase, guaranteeing seamless integration with your device.,?? Stain Resistant Surface: Delight in a surface that defies stains, thanks to the revolutionary SemiSi-tech technology by GreenLaw seamlessly blended with PU leather. Experience a soft, sweat-resistant touch that not only feels premium but also allows for effortless stain removal. The plush fleece lining adds an extra layer of care, ensuring your iPad 10th generation stays flawless, and no worry from scratches.,?? Magnetic Floating Stand: Transform your daily experience with the magic-like floating stand, a pinnacle of modern functionality. Boasting a robust magnetic matrix of 31 magnets, it provides a secure attachment with an impressive force of up to 2600GS. What sets it apart is its exceptional durability  rigorously tested to withstand 15,000 bending cycles. Immerse yourself in the convenience of a stable and effortlessly adjustable stand, backed by unparalleled strength and longevity.,?? Seamless Bluetooth Connectivity? Experience low-power Bluetooth stability powered by the cutting-edge Bluetooth 5.2 chip. Simply pair your iPad 10th gen. 2022 with the keyboard, and relish in the convenience of automatic reconnection for everyday use. Enjoy a reliable and latency-free connection that seamlessly integrates with your iPad, enhancing your daily productivity with effortless connectivity.,? Typing with Scissor-Style Switches: Indulge in the pleasure of comfortable typing with the scissor-style switch keys. Revel in the swift and instant rebound of each keystroke, coupled with a comfortable 1 mm key travel. Immerse yourself in a sensitive, comfortable, and quiet typing journey on your iPad 2022, boosting your productivity effortlessly.,?? Vibrant Backlight Customization: Infuse your workspace with personality using the backlight selection. Unleash your creativity by choosing from 7 vivid colors across 3 brightness levels, empowering you to tailor the perfect ambiance for your typing experience with iPad 10th Generation Case with Keyboard. Elevate your keyboard aesthetics and create an atmosphere that complements your unique style, making every typing session a visually delightful experience.,??? Intuitive Touchpad: Navigate effortlessly with our intuitive touchpad, supporting multi-touch gestures. Swipe to return to the main screen or switch between spaces, unlocking a new realm of control gestures for a seamless and efficient user experience.,?? Intelligent Charging and Power Management: Experience convenience with USB-C charging, intelligent battery management, and a smart sleep mode. With one-touch wake-up functionality, our keyboard ensures efficient power usage, providing peace of mind and uninterrupted productivity wherever you go.

name: PRITOM Android Tablet 10 inch, M10, 2 GB RAM, 32 GB Android 10.0 Tablet, 10.1 inch IPS HD Display, GPS, FM, Quad-Core Processor, Wi-Fi (M10 Black)
feature_bullets: High Performance Android Table -Pritom Tronpad tablet comes with the latest Android 10.0 , The powerful and energy-saving 32 bit Quad-core processor 1. 5GHz, 2GB RAM,enables quicker app launch, smoother videos and better overall performance. In addition, it includes a micro SD card slot (can be added a 128 GB SD card Max, NOT included), no more worrying about storage space, making it easy to store videos etc.,Native and Latest Android - Android 10.0: 5000mAh lithium polymer battery and low-power CPU enhance your experience and allow you to enjoy up to 6 hours of mixed reading, watching TV shows, surfing the web, playing light games and more. It is a really good companion for you,Stunning IPS Display-The 10 inch tablet adopts a 1280 x 800 IPS display, which presents a sharper hierarchy of images and richer colors for a more true-to-life viewing experience from all angles.Read comfortably at night with Eye Health, an extra feature that automatically adjusts and optimizes the backlight for a more comfortable nighttime reading experience.,32GB ROM with Expandable Memory-The tablet offers 32GB of onboard memory and includes a microSD card slot (microSD card sold separately) that allows you to add up to an additional 128GB of memory, keep all your favorite media with you wherever you go, such as eBooks, songs, videos, photos, music, etc.,Tablet equipped with HD IPS 1280 x 800 pixel touch screen. The IPS screen can show clear and stable images and help you not feel eye fatigue after using the tablet for a long time. Lightweight body is suitable for carrying.

name: Moderness Tablet 10.1 Inch Android 12 Quad Core 32GB ROM 1280x800 IPS Display 5000mAh Tablets PC Gray
feature_bullets: ?[Excellent Performance] This Tablet PC runs on the latest Android 12 operating system and has 2GB RAM & 32GB ROM. The powerful and energy-saving 64-bit quad-core processor (up to 1.6GHz) provides strong performance and increases app startup speed.,?[High-performance Processor]The tablet is lightweight, and the quad-core processor enables an impressive multimedia experience. With a 5000mAh lithium polymer battery and low power consumption CPU, you can enjoy up to 6 hours of video watching or 18 hours of music playback.,?[Clear and bright IPS display] This 10.1 inch tablet computer uses a 1280*800 HD IPS display with vivid colors and an improved viewing angle. Enjoy immersive reading on the large-screen display, and use reading mode to watch comfortably at night. Reading mode is a feature that automatically adjusts and optimizes the backlight to reduce eye fatigue.,?[Dual Camera and Dual Box Speakers] Take photos and videos with the front 2.0 MP and rear 5.0 MP cameras. It lets you conveniently take pictures and share them with friends and family. Our tablet also uses dual box speakers, allowing for higher volume and sound quality and also reducing distortion to give you a better listening experience.,?[Special Gift] This tablets durable silver casing and sleek design makes it great for the office or to give as a gift. We offer a 1-year return and exchange service. To ensure your satisfaction, please contact us if you have other questions about this tablet.

name: Lville Android 13 Tablet, Octa-Core Android Tablet, 8 (4+4) RAM 128GB ROM (1TB TF) Tablet Android, 10 inch Tablet with WiFi 6, Bluetooth5.0, Dual Camera, Fast Charging (Gray)
feature_bullets: ??Latest Android 13.0 Tablet?This tablet comes with a powerful Android 13.0 system, which brings you a whole new task bar experience and a more user-friendly UI with enhanced customization options. Android 13 also emphasizes privacy and security by designing enhanced app permissions, giving users complete management control. It places a greater focus on user privacy and offers heightened security measures.,??Fast Connection & Smoother Sensitive Experience?The android tablet is equipped with a powerful A55 architecture and an Octa-core CPU, delivering a smooth and fast performance and convenient operations. Whether you're watching videos, browsing the web, or listening to music, you'll enjoy a seamless and uninterrupted experience.,??2023's latest Version 8 (4+4) GB + 128GB + 1TB Expandable? This 10-inch tablet comes with 8GB (4GB +4GB expansion) RAM, 128GB ROM and a micro-SD card slot that allows for an expansion of 1TB of memory. Large and expandable storage can run more smoothly and you can quickly launch applications and enjoy it without the stress of running out of storage space. Feel free to download any app you want.,??10.1-inch IPS & Long-Life Battery?The tablet android equipped with a high resolution 1280*800 IPS display, which shows a brightly colored wide-screen for a more realistic viewing experience with sharper and brighter images. This 10-inch android tablet also equipped with a rechargeable battery up to 5000mAh, it lasts for up to 8 hours on a single charge. Using the Type-C port to charge more easily, regardless of positive or negative. Allow you to work or play all day while you're on the road.,??Perfect Choice for Everyday Use?The android tablets with lightweight and slim design, only 8mm thin body, allows you to enjoy e-books, movies, TV shows and music effortlessly while traveling or on business trips. We provide a one-year warranty for the OC101 Android 13 tablet. If any quality issues arise, please contact us through your Amazon purchase records and we will work to ensure customer satisfaction.

name: KENKE iPad 10th Generation Case with Keyboard 10.9 inch 2022, Detachable Wireless Bluetooth iPad Keyboard Case Thin & Light with Built-in Left Side Pencil Holder Auto Wake/Sleep (Gray
feature_bullets: ???Compatibility Model?This iPad case with keyboard is designed for iPad 10th Generation 2022 10.9 inch. ( Model: A2696/A2757/A2777 ). NOT compatible with any other iPad models. Please check the back bottom of your iPad to find the model number before placing order.,???Slim Wireless Bluetooth Keyboard?The slim (6.2mm) removable keyboard is attached to this iPad cover with keyboard magnetically (supporting Windows, IOS & Android System), let your ipad instantly become a portable laptop, perfect for working, typing, editing or watching videos, greatly improved your iPad productivity.,???Long Battery Life & Multi Angle Support?Built-in industry-high rechargeable Li-polymer battery make the wireless keyboard of this 10th gen iPad case with keyboard stand by for more than 3 days after 2-3 hours of full charge. The protective shell can be placed at different tilt angles to adjust the optimal viewing angle, very flexible and user-friendly.,???Buit-in Pencil Slot & Sturdy PU Material?The iPad 10th generation keyboard case has a convenient left side built-in pencil slot that easy to storage and remove your pencil (Apple Pencil is Not included). Premium PU leather cover is waterproof, scratch proof and fingerprint proof, providing full protection for your beloved tablet.,???Packing List & Considerate Customer Service? 1 x apple iPad 10th generation case with keyboard, 1 x Wireless Keyboard, 1x USB charging cord, 1 x user guide. As a reliable brand, we are very concerned about the reputation & quality of our products. Any question dont hesitate to contact us.

name: Logitech Combo Touch iPad Air (4th, 5th gen - 2020, 2022) Keyboard Case - Oxford Grey (Renewed)
feature_bullets: Compatible with iPad Air (4th and 5th generation - 2020, 2022) - A2316, A2324, A2325, A2072.Viewing Angles: 10°-60°,Do it all with Combo Touch: Four versatile use modes allow you to type, sketch, view and read without ever having to remove your iPad Air from the keyboard case,Detachable keyboard and adjustable kickstand: Remove the keyboard when you're done typing for more flexibility and enjoy 50 degrees of adjustable viewing angles,Large, click-anywhere trackpad: This iPad keyboard case features a responsive and reliable trackpad that allows you to use the entire surface to work and perform Multi-Touch trackpad gestures,Backlit, laptop-like keyboard: Backlit keys auto-adjust to your environment with 16 levels of brightness and a full row of iPadOS shortcut keys provide one-tap access to volume controls and more,Front, back and corner protection: A durable form-fit cover protects the front, back, and corners of your iPad Air, securely holding it in place no matter what youre doing,SMART CONNECTOR technology: Enjoy instant power and pairing with Combo Touch keyboard case and never worry about charging as power is sourced directly from your iPad Air,Home for Apple Pencil: Easily charge your Apple Pencil while keeping the case on thanks to a convenient opening in the side of the iPad Air case

name: Apple iPad (10th Generation): with A14 Bionic chip, 10.9-inch Liquid Retina Display, 64GB, Wi-Fi 6, 12MP front/12MP Back Camera, Touch ID, All-Day Battery Life  Blue
feature_bullets: WHY IPAD  Colorfully reimagined and more versatile than ever, iPad is great for the things you do every day. With an all-screen design, 10.9-inch Liquid Retina display, powerful A14 Bionic chip, superfast Wi-Fi, and four gorgeous colors, iPad delivers a powerful way to create, stay connected, and get things done.,IPADOS + APPS  iPadOS makes iPad more productive, intuitive, and versatile. With iPadOS, run multiple apps at once, use Apple Pencil to write in any text field with Scribble, and edit and share photos. iPad comes with essential apps like Safari, Messages, and Keynote, with over a million more apps available on the App Store.,FAST WI-FI CONNECTIVITY  Wi-Fi 6 gives you fast access to your files, uploads, and downloads, and lets you seamlessly stream your favorite shows.,PERFORMANCE AND STORAGE  The A14 Bionic chip delivers power and performance for any activity. And with all-day battery life, iPad is perfect for playing immersive games and editing photos and videos. Choose from 64GB or 256GB storage options.,APPLE PENCIL AND MAGIC KEYBOARD FOLIO  With Apple Pencil (1st generation), iPad transforms into an immersive drawing canvas and the worlds best note?taking device. The Magic Keyboard Folio features a versatile two-piece design with a detachable keyboard and a protective back panel that both attach magnetically to iPad. Accessories sold separately.,10.9-INCH LIQUID RETINA DISPLAY  The gorgeous Liquid Retina display is an amazing way to watch movies or draw your next masterpiece. True Tone adjusts the display to the color temperature of the room to make viewing comfortable in any light.,UNLOCK AND PAY WITH TOUCH ID  Touch ID is built into the top button, so you can use your fingerprint to unlock your iPad, sign in to apps, and make payments securely with Apple Pay.,ADVANCED CAMERAS  iPad features a landscape 12MP Ultra Wide front camera that supports Center Stage for videoconferencing and selfies. Shoot 4K video or photos with the 12MP Wide back camera, then edit right on your iPad.,LEGAL DISCLAIMERS  This is a summary of the main product features.

name: Apple iPad (9th Generation): with A13 Bionic chip, 10.2-inch Retina Display, 64GB, Wi-Fi, 12MP front/8MP Back Camera, Touch ID, All-Day Battery Life  Silver
feature_bullets: WHY IPAD  All the essentials in the most affordable iPad, with a beautiful 10.2-inch Retina display, powerful A13 Bionic chip, and an Ultra Wide front camera with Center Stage. Work, play, create, learn, stay connected, and more.,IPADOS + APPS  iPadOS makes iPad more productive, intuitive, and versatile. With iPadOS, run multiple apps at once, use Apple Pencil to write in any text field with Scribble, and edit and share photos. iPad comes with essential apps like Safari, Messages, and Keynote, with over a million more apps available on the App Store.,FAST WI-FI CONNECTIVITY  Fast Wi-Fi keeps you connected at home, work, school, or wherever you go with your iPad.,PERFORMANCE AND STORAGE  The A13 Bionic chip gives you the graphics performance you need. And with all-day battery life, iPad is perfect for playing immersive games and more. Choose from 64GB or 256GB storage options.,APPLE PENCIL AND SMART KEYBOARD  Apple Pencil (1st generation) transforms iPad into an immersive drawing canvas and the worlds best note?taking device. The Smart Keyboard features a comfortable typing experience and folds into a slim, lightweight cover for protection. Accessories sold separately,10.2-INCH RETINA DISPLAY  With incredible detail and vivid colors, its perfect for watching movies or drawing your next masterpiece. True Tone adjusts the display to the color temperature of the room to make viewing comfortable in any light.,UNLOCK AND PAY WITH TOUCH ID  Touch ID is built into the top button, so you can use your fingerprint to unlock your iPad, sign in to apps, and make payments securely with Apple Pay.,FRONT AND BACK CAMERAS  iPad features a 12MP Ultra Wide front camera that supports Center Stage for videoconferencing and selfies. The 8MP Wide back camera is perfect for capturing photos, 1080p HD video, and scanning documents.,LEGAL DISCLAIMERS  This is a summary of the main product features.

name: 2024 Newest Tablet 10 inch 12GB RAM + 128GB ROM (1TB TF) Android 13 Cores 2.0Ghz, WiFi 5G+2.4G, Bluetooth 5.0, GPS, Google GMS, 8000mAh Battery, 8+5MP, Metal Body, with Case, Keyboard and Mouse, Gold
feature_bullets: ?The latest Android 13 and 2.0 GHz Processors?The J10 tablet is equipped with the Android 13 system. The new system enhances privacy and data protection, making it faster and more secure. Android 13 brings you more personalized settings (Widgets, split screen, parental controls and multiple users, etc.). The tablet is equipped with a powerful 2.0Ghz processor that provides a smooth and secure experience for using the system and streaming media,?12GB RAM + 128GB ROM + 1TB Expandable?The J10 tablet is equipped with 12GB RAM (6GB RAM + 6GB RAM expansion) and 128GB ROM, which supports maximum memory expansion of 1TB (via MicroSD/TF card), and this memory can be configured as additional memory/portable memory. Tablets offer ample space for running applications or storing photos, films, documents and books,?Dual Wi-Fi and Bluetooth 5.0?The tablet supports 2.4 Ghz and 5 Ghz Wi-Fi, a new Wi-Fi reception and transmission channel, which improves network connection speed and stability. GOOGLE Play is preinstalled and various apps can be downloaded from the Play Store. The tablet has a more stable and faster built-in Bluetooth 5.0 function, which can connect Bluetooth headsets, Bluetooth keyboards and other Bluetooth devices via Bluetooth 5.0,?10-inch Screen and 8000mAh Battery?J10 uses a 10-inch 2.5D screen, which effectively improves screen sensitivity and touch comfort. You can deliver clear, rich colors in different environments and filter out blue light. The tablet is equipped with 5MP + 8MP front and rear cameras, which can make video calls with your family, friends and colleagues. The high-capacity 8000 mAh battery provides peak power to the tablet,?Tablet with Metal Body and Laptop 2 in 1?J10 adopts an aluminum alloy body, lightweight, high strength and elegant appearance. The tablet package contains a J10 tablet, mouse, Bluetooth keyboard, OTG adapter, case, charger, SD ejector pin, screen protector, etc. You can configure the tablet as a small laptop. name: Amazon Fire HD 8 tablet, 8 HD Display, 32 GB, 30% faster processor, designed for portable entertainment, (2022 release), Black
feature_bullets: Enhanced performance - Updated hexa-core processor for more responsive performance (up to 30% faster than previous gen Fire HD 8).,All day battery life - Up to 13 hours of reading, browsing the web, watching videos, and listening to music at home and on-the-go.,Stream or download your favorite shows and movies from Prime Video, Netflix, Disney+, and HBO. Enjoy your favorite content from Facebook, Hulu, Instagram, TikTok, and more through Amazons Appstore (Google Play not supported. Subscription for some apps required).,Fire HD 8 offers 8" HD display and 2 GB RAM. Choose from 32GB or 64GB (up to 1TB of expandable storage via microSD card). New design is thinner and lighter than previous gen. Screen made with strengthened aluminosilicate glass. As measured in tumble tests, Fire HD 8 is twice as durable as Apple iPad mini (2021).,Stay connected with family and friends - ask Alexa to make video calls to friends and family or download apps like Zoom.,Do more with Alexa - Ask Alexa to listen to music, get news and weather, update shopping lists, and set reminders. Control your smart home, or ask Alexa to make video calls to friends and family with apps like Zoom.,Amazon Kids offers easy-to-use parental controls on Fire tablets. Subscribe to Amazon Kids+ for access to thousands of books, popular apps and games, videos, songs, Audible books, and more.

name: iPad Charger, [ MFi Certified ] 10 FT Long iPad Chargers Lightning Cord Cable Fast Charging USB Wall Charger Block Foldable Plug for iPad 7th 8th 9th Generation, iPad Air, iPad Mini, iPad Pro, iPhone
feature_bullets: ???iPad Charger Foldable Plug?With 100-240 volt input and replaceable iPad charger block, this iPad iPhone Charger is ideal for worldwide travel. Designed for avoiding any possible scratch damage in your pocket, the 90 degrees foldable block is perfect for use both at home and on the go. Besides, quick-charge USB port provides Max output power, charge your devices up to 2.5x faster than original 5W charger saving over 1 hour for you.,???10 ft Long Lightning Cord?You could connect your MacBook/Pro with iPhone/iPad directly and enjoy the 480 Mbps data transfer speed. Tangle-free 10 Foot length is convenient for usage while charging and sync at home/office/travel in bed, hotel rooms, and more.,???MFI Certified iPad Lightning Charger?MFi is a kind of express license for external accessories produced by authorized accessory manufacturers. It is the abbreviation of Made for iPhone / iPod / iPad.The certification test process is extremely demanding, with a pass rate of only 2%. With our MFI approved chargers for iPads and iPhones, no more trigger warning messages pops up.,???Applicable Equipments? 2021 iPad 9th generation/2020 iPad 8th generation/2019 iPad 7th generation/2018 iPad 6th generation/2017 iPad 5th generation/2012 iPad 4th generation/2019 iPad Mini 5th generation/2015 iPad Mini 4th generation/2014 iPad Mini 3rd generation/2013 iPad Mini 2nd generation/2012 iPad Mini 1st generation/2019 iPad Air 3rd generation/2014 iPad Air 2nd generation/2013 iPad Air 1st generation/2017 iPad Pro 12.9 inch/2015 iPad Pro 12.9 inch/2017 iPad Pro 10.5 inch/2016 iPad Pro 9.7 inch/iPhone/AirPods,???What You Get?1 * iPad Charger Fast Charging Block, 1 * 10FT USB to Lightning iPad Charger Cord Cable , 24 hours friendly customer service.

name: SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab S9 FE Wi-Fi 10.9 128GB Android Tablet, IP68 Water- and Dust-Resistant, Long Battery Life, Powerful Processor, S Pen, 8MP Camera, Lightweight Design, US Version, 2023, Silver
feature_bullets: A SCREEN FOR ALL YOUR ADVENTURES: Start every adventure with a large, beautiful 10.9" screen*. Whether youre a multitasker, a gamer or a devoted movie watcher, youll feel closer to the action. Plus, dual speakers make everything sound amazing,BUILT FOR ADVENTURE: An IP68 rating makes Galaxy Tab S9 FE one of the only water- and dust-resistant** tablets on the market. Its built to last wherever you use it, making it a great choice for first-time tablet buyers,A BATTERY THAT KEEPS YOU IN CHARGE: With a tablet this powerful, portable and fun, youll never want to put it down. Go up to 18 hours*** with a long-lasting battery and get a full charge in less than 90 minutes with Super Fast Charging****,POWER FOR ADVENTURE: The latest Exynos chipset lets you own the day and stay in touch. Cross off your to-do list and video chat with your college roomie miles away. Whatever youre doing, Galaxy Tab S9 FE makes for rich experiences,SMART TECH, BEAUTIFULLY MADE: Galaxy Tab S9 FE complements your personality perfectly. Plus, with a refined design thats sleek and lightweight, youll be able to show off your great taste anywhere you use your Tab,PEN-POINT PRECISION: Theres virtually no limit to what you can do with S Pen. Write notes by hand. Draw a comic strip or mark up a document. Pen features a responsive design that feels like youre writing on actual paper,STORAGE FOR ALL YOUR ADVENTURES: Lifes an adventure, so keep track of your favorite moments with up to 256GB***** of storage. Thats plenty of space and if you need more room, add up to 1TB more with a microSD card******,CAMERAS BUILT FOR VIDEO CHAT: Collaborate effortlessly with a camera that automatically adjusts to keep the focus on you*******. Plus, with a large display that opens up to 3 apps at once, you can multitask while you video chat,FILE SHARING MADE EASY: Sending and receiving files is so easy with Quick Share********. From selfie videos to large work files, transfer to and from your Galaxy Tab S9 FE in a snap  it even works when sending to non-Galaxy devices,TAKE CALLS FROM YOUR TAB: When youre fully immersed in a project, sometimes you dont want to stop to switch gears; With the Galaxy Connected Experience, you can take calls or texts directly from your Tab without interrupting your flow*********

name: Maxsignage Android 13 Tablet, 10.1" HD Screen, Octa-core Processor with 8(4+4) GB&64GB Storage, Expandable Memory to 128GB, Support WiFi 6 and Bluetooth 5.0, 5000 mAh Battery, Google GMS Certified
feature_bullets: Pushing the Performance Limits  With a cutting-edge octa-core processor, Android 13 delivers unparalleled tabletas performance. Effortlessly handle multitasking and power-hungry applications, making every interaction a seamless experience.,Endurance Redefined  Fueled by a robust 5000mAh battery,5-8 hours for use enjoy extended windows tablet usage without the anxiety of running out of power. Dive into your digital world with confidence, knowing your device can keep up with your demands.,Ample Memory, Limitless Potential  Boasting a 8(4+4)&64GB memory configuration, Maxsignage Android tablet provides expansive storage to accommodate files, apps, and cherished moments. Free up your imagination and revel in the possibilities of a spacious digital canvas.,Visual Brilliance in 1080P  Immerse yourself in the stunning visuals of a 1080P high-definition screen. Every frame comes to life with vibrant colors and captivating details, offering a visual feast that transcends ordinary 10 inch tablet displays.,Rapid Connectivity, Boundless Possibilities  Featuring WiFi 6 and Bluetooth 5.0 technology, Our tab ensures lightning-fast and stable wireless connections. Experience high-speed internet and connect with a wider range of Bluetooth devices, breaking free from connectivity constraints.

name: Android 13 Tablet 2023 New 10 Inch Tablets with 6GB RAM + 64GB ROM + 1TB Expanded Ouad-Core, 2 in 1 Tablet with Keyboard Mouse WiFi 6 Bluetooth, GMS Certified IPS Touch Screen Tablet - Black Set
feature_bullets: 2-in-1 Android Tablet - Our versatile tablet effortlessly transforms from a tablet to a portable laptop with the included mouse and keyboard, you can use it easily for productivity while on the move or switch to tablet mode to enjoy entertainment.,Android 13 Tablet with GMS Certification - The tablet is powered by the latest Android 13 operating system. It offers an easy-to-use interface and access to a wide range of apps, games and services through Google Play Store. You can keep up with the latest features and experience a seamless and simple user experience.,10.1 Inch HD Screen - Immerse yourself in breathtaking visuals on the expansive 10.1 inch high definition IPS display. Featuring a resolution of 1280*800, every image and video bursts with vibrant hues and pristine clarity.,6GB RAM & 64GB ROM - Allow you to multitask and store important data, pictures and videos,you can even add a 1TB Micro SD card for more storage.,Dual Cameras and more - ECOPAD android tablet features a 2MP front camera and an 8MP rear camera, supporting 2.4GHz WiFi / WiFi 6 and Bluetooth 5.0. It has a built-in 6000mAh lithium battery for reliable all-day performance.

name: Tablet 10.1 inch Android 12 Tablet 2023 Latest Update Octa-Core Processor with 64GB Storage, Dual 13MP+5MP Camera, WiFi, Bluetooth, GPS, 512GB Expand Support, IPS Full HD Display (Black)
feature_bullets: ?SUPERIOR WATCHING EXPERIENCE?FEONAL Tablet is powered by Octa-Core Processor. 2023 newest Android 12 tablet provides + 40% faster processing speed than regular Quad-Core. 10.1-inch Tablet screen size with 1920x1200 resolution support, perfect for home entertainment and office.,?BIGGER THAN BIGGER?The tablet has 4GB RAM, 64GB internal storage and expandable storage up to 128 GB. The GMS Certified latest Android Tablet, with basic Google apps already on and without bloatware. Get rid of unexpected ads and download apps from Google Play, such as SKYGO, NetFlix, YouTube and more.,?LONG LASTING BATTERY?Equipped with a long-lasting and environmentally compliant 6000 mAh battery, this 10-inch tablet will effortlessly provide you with up to 8 hours of support for reading, browsing, watching movies and playing games. The long-lasting battery life and lightweight design allow you to enjoy your tablet anywhere, anytime.,?DUAL CAMERAS AND SPEAKERS?With front 5 MP & Rear 13 MP dual cameras, which would bring your excellent photos and clear video chats. Dual speakers are designed to provide high-quality and powerful sound for your favorite music, games and videos.,?IDEAL CHOICE FOR GIFT?FEONAL 10'' Android Tablet is definitely the best choice for Christmas or Valentine's Day. We provide professional tablet for 5 years with considerate service, please feel free to contact our customer service if you have any problems.

feature_bullets: ?Android 12 OS & 8GB RAM 128GB ROM?The TYD-109 android tablet runs on Android 12 system and is loaded with an 8GB of RAM and 128GB of ROM for storing all your apps, files, and media. This tablet is perfect for playing large games and loading large data. It has lightning-fast speed and smooth performance. You will find that web pages load without any lagging and apps open in a snap. Whether you're streaming videos, playing games or working on important documents, this tablet handles every task easily.,?10.1 inch FHD IPS tablet + wireless projection + 5MP/13MP Camera? The tablet has a 10.1 inch 1920*1200 resolution. Wide viewing angle IPS FHD screen, you can enjoy more real and shocking images. It supports wireless projection (not HDMI) for easy connection to a big TV. Face recognition, unlocking is more convenient and intelligent. With 5MP + 13MP camera, microphone, Type-C charging port, dual-band Wi-Fi and BT 5.0, it has everything you need for virtual learning and video calling on the go,?Google GMS Certification & Max-Expandable 1TB?This Tablets is equipped with 128GB ROM Built-in memory, supports 1TB (1024GB) capacity expansion, includes a micro SD slot, allows you to download a lot of applications from Google Play Store and have fun with them. The android tablet has passed the Google GMS certification. You have full access to the latest Google service, such as Google Play, WhatsApp, G-mail, Skype, Disney+, Netflix, YouTube, ZOOM, Google Assistant and more brilliant apps,?2.4G/5G Wifi + 8000mAh + GPS?Tablets with AC dual-band 2.5+5G WiFi, providing an ast Internet experience with less radio interference. 8000mAh and a low-power processor. Achieve up to 10 hours of video battery life. It also has GPS, you can use Google Maps if you download offline maps to your tablet. The 10.1 inch tablet adopts metal body and stylish blue. The smooth touch makes it easy to hold. With a weight of 530g, it is very convenient to carry whether you are working, studying or going out,Compatibility and Better Service The tablet supports google-certified GMS software, which allows you to download a range of android apps from Google apps.If you have any problem with the product, please feel free to contact us. TYD's customer service ensures that you can provide a satisfactory solution

name: ZAGG Rugged Book iPad Case with Detachable Magnetic-Hinged Keyboard for iPad Air 3, iPad Pro 10.5", and 10.2" (9th Gen), Multi-Device Bluetooth, Apple Pencil Holder, Long-Lasting Battery,Black
feature_bullets: TOUGH, VERSATILE IPAD CASE & KEYBOARD - Featuring a magnetic hinge, the ZAGG Rugged Book holds your tablet securely and lets you adjust the viewing angle for maximum productivity. Compatible with Apple iPad Air 3, iPad 10.2" and iPad Pro 10.5" (9th Gen).Number of buttons: 78,INCREDIBLE TYPING EXPERIENCE - The new, ergonomic Pro keyframe design offers smooth, precise key travel for fast, accurate touch typing. With backlighting in 7 colors, the laptop-style, low-profile keys make typing comfortable even in low-light conditions,RUGGED, DURABLE DESIGN - Made from polycarbonate & soft silicone materials, the iPad holder protects your device from scratches & scuffs. Take your iPad on every adventure & make any environment your workspace, with the ultimate 6.6ft (2m) drop protection,EXTRAORDINARY FEATURES - With Bluetooth multi-device pairing, you can connect up to 2 devices simultaneously and toggle back and forth between them. The keyboard is also equipped with forward-facing speaker cutouts and a holder for Apple Pencil or stylus,LONG LASTING BATTERY - The rechargeable battery keeps the Rugged Book up and running for up to 2 years between charges (battery life depends on duration and backlight usage). The sleep/wake function helps preserve battery when the keyboard is not in use

name: SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab S7 FE 12.4 256GB WiFi Android Tablet, Large Screen, S Pen Included, Multi Device Connectivity, Long Lasting Battery, US Version, 2021, Mystic Green
feature_bullets: CNET BEST PICK: CNET (12/22) picked Samsung Galaxy Tab S7 FE as "Best Android Tablet for 2023, highlighting its premium look and feel for significantly less money.,BIG SCREEN, BIG EXPERIENCE: A large 12.4 inch display brings your content to life in brilliant color whether indoors or outdoors, making Samsung Galaxy S7 FE a great tablet for study time or for a quick entertainment break,BOLD COLORS, BOLD STATEMENT: Choose a bold color  Mystic Black, Mystic Green, Mystic Silver or Mystic Pink  that makes it unmistakably yours,WRITE, DRAW, CLIP, TAP WITH S PEN: Take notes in class, sketch out an idea or even doodle with the included S Pen, featuring a responsive new design that feels closer to pen on paper than ever before,MORE WORKSPACE, MORE WAYS TO WORK: Master every assignment with Galaxy connectivity; Get more done on an expanded workstation that lets you hand off content between your devices, or enjoy a PC like experience with multiple windows open on your tablet,POWERED TO DO MORE: Galaxy Tab S7 FE features a long battery life* to help you power through your day  and then some  on a single charge,SPEED TO MOVE, SPACE TO GROW: With the Qualcomm SM7225 Octa-Core processor, youll enjoy smooth entertainment; Plus, high storage memory lets you save and store what you need to access on a moments notice,STREAM YOUR HEART OUT, 160+ CHANNELS: Unwind with two months of ad free access to millions of videos with YouTube Premium*; Also get free access to Samsung Mobile TV Plus, and over 160 channels and videos on demand, such as movies, music, news and sports

name: Samsung Galaxy Tab A7 Lite 8.7" (2021, WiFi + Cellular) 32GB 4G LTE Tablet & Phone (Makes Calls) GSM Unlocked, International Model w/US Charging Cube - SM-T225 (Grey, LTE+WiFi)
feature_bullets: 8.7", 800 x 1340, 5:3 ratio, WXGA+, TFT, Android 11, One UI 3.1, Face Recognition, 5100mAh Battery,32GB ROM, 3GB RAM, Mediatek MT8768T Helio P22T (12 nm), Octa-core, PowerVR GE8320,Rear Camera: 8MP, Front Camera: 2MP, 5,100mAh, Bluetooth v5.0, Wi-Fi: 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac 2.4G + 5GHz,2G GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900, 3G HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1700(AWS) / 1900 / 2100, 4G LTE B1(2100), B2(1900), B3(1800), B4(AWS), B5(850), B7(2600), B8(900), B12(700), B17(700), B20(800), B28(700), B38(2600), B40(2300), B66(AWS-3),International Model, Does not have US Warranty. This tablet is unlocked to work with all GSM Carriers in the U.S. and world Including AT&T, T-Mobile, MetroPCS, Etc. Will NOT work with CDMA Carriers Such as Verizon, Sprint, Boost.

name: UMIDIGI Kids Tablet, G1 Tab Android 13 Tablet PC, 10.1" Tablet for Kids, 8G+64G up to 1TB, WiFi 6, 8MP+8MP Dual Camera, Quad-Core, 6000mAh, BT5.0, TÜV Eye Bluelight Tablet Android, Parental Control
feature_bullets: ?The Latest Android 13 + WIFI 6?UMIDIGI G1 TAB tablet is equipped with the latest Android 13 system, and a built-in RK3562 Quad-Core chip with 2.0GHz frequency, providing you with a super smooth experience. G1 Tab also supports Wi-Fi 6 with transmission speeds up to 9.6Gbps. With better penetration, less signal loss, and longer propagation distance, supporting both 2.4G and 5G bands, enjoy faster transfer speeds and a better video experience.,?8GB (4+4 expansion) RAM + 64GB ROM + 1TB TF?The G1 Tab Android 13 tablet uses the latest memory expansion technology to dramatically increase the memory running space from 4GB to 8GB, allowing the tablet to open more applications at the same time, and running at maximum efficiency. The Android kids tablet comes with 64GB ROM and up to 1TB of expandable microSD storage for even more space.,?10.1inch Full View Display + Bluetooth5.0 + Intelligent Split Screen? The 1280*800 HD IPS touch screen provide richer and more vibrant colors for excellent visual effects for your kids. The smart split-screen feature creates dual windows at the same time to easily handle more problems and increase productivity, allowing you to take online courses, make video calls, and perform a wide range of business and creative tasks simultaneously.,?Dual Camera + Large-Capacity Battery?G1 Tab with excellent 8MP rear camera + 8MP front camera, easy to record daily life and enhance parent-child interaction; 6000mAh large-capacity battery and intelligent power saving tech, with 550 hours of standby time, 52 hours of talk time and 15 hours of playtime, you can travel and hike with confidence.,?Parental Control Mode+EVA Protective Case?This Kid's Tablet laptop features powerful parental control. Kids Park parental control allows you to filter content based on a child's age, set educational goals and screen time limits, and grant access to additional content. Exit the child mode interface and you can use it as a normal Android tablet. The G1 Tab tablet computer comes with a fully enclosed, non-toxic EVA case. ????G1 Kids Tablet does not support face recognition, only password unlocking

name: Logitech Combo Touch iPad Air (4th, 5th gen - 2020, 2022) Keyboard Case - Oxford Grey (Renewed)
feature_bullets: Compatible with iPad Air (4th and 5th generation - 2020, 2022) - A2316, A2324, A2325, A2072.Viewing Angles: 10°-60°,Do it all with Combo Touch: Four versatile use modes allow you to type, sketch, view and read without ever having to remove your iPad Air from the keyboard case,Detachable keyboard and adjustable kickstand: Remove the keyboard when you're done typing for more flexibility and enjoy 50 degrees of adjustable viewing angles,Large, click-anywhere trackpad: This iPad keyboard case features a responsive and reliable trackpad that allows you to use the entire surface to work and perform Multi-Touch trackpad gestures,Backlit, laptop-like keyboard: Backlit keys auto-adjust to your environment with 16 levels of brightness and a full row of iPadOS shortcut keys provide one-tap access to volume controls and more,Front, back and corner protection: A durable form-fit cover protects the front, back, and corners of your iPad Air, securely holding it in place no matter what youre doing,SMART CONNECTOR technology: Enjoy instant power and pairing with Combo Touch keyboard case and never worry about charging as power is sourced directly from your iPad Air,Home for Apple Pencil: Easily charge your Apple Pencil while keeping the case on thanks to a convenient opening in the side of the iPad Air case

name: SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab A8 10.5 32GB Android Tablet, LCD Screen, Kids Content, Smart Switch, Expandable Memory, Long Lasting Battery, Fast Charging, US Version, 2022, Silver, Amazon Exclusive
feature_bullets: A SCREEN EVERYONE WILL LOVE: Whether your family is streaming or video chatting with friends, the Galaxy Tab A8 tablet brings out the best in every moment on a 10.5" LCD screen,POWER AND STORAGE FOR ALL: Get the power, storage and speed your family needs with an upgraded chipset and plenty of room to keep files  up to 128GB of storage; A long-lasting battery lets you go unplugged for hours to keep the family fun going,CHARGE FAST, POWER FOR HOURS: Go for hours on a single charge and back to 100% with the fast charging USB C port; Battery life may vary depending on network environment, usage patterns and other factors,GALAXY ECOSYSTEM EXPERIENCE: Open up a new world of convenient possibilities with the Galaxy ecosystem experience  your devices, including your phone, laptop computer, and tablet, all automatically talk to one another seamlessly,YOUR NOTES, ALL IN ONE PLACE: Do more with your notes with Galaxy connectivity that automatically syncs everything from to-do lists to school work, whether youre on your tablet, phone or watch,KIDS DIGITAL LEARNING: Children can enjoy access to Samsung Kids, a library of safe and fun games, books and videos that are kid friendly and parent approved,EASIEST. TRANSFER. EVER: No matter what operating system you're using, Smart Switch makes it a breeze to move your data and favorite files in three easy steps

name: SGIN 10.1 Inch Tablet Android 12 Tablets with 8GB RAM 128GB ROM, MTK Octa-Core 2.0Ghz Processor, 1280 * 800 HD IPS Srceen, 5MP+8MP Camera, WiFi, Bluetooth, 6000mAh, Black
feature_bullets: ?Full HD IPS Screen 10 inch Tablet?This 10 in tablet is equipped with a 10.1 inch high definition 1280*800 IPS screen with a narrow bezel design giving it more screen-to-body ratio and built-in dual speakers to provide you with more stunning auditory and visual effects. Perfect for watching movies, playing games, browsing the web, or working online.,?8GB+128GB Large-Capacity Tablets?This android tablet 10 inch is equipped with 8GB high-speed LPDDR4 random-access memory, enable to quicker launch speed, smoother interacting with the WiFi tablet. 128GB large-capacity storage space, supporting 256GB TF card expansion. you can store as many ebooks, songs, pictures, videos, and games as you like and complete a variety of tasks.,?High-Performance Android 12 tablet?This tablet android is equipped with MT8183, with a high-performance 8-core CPU that has a frequency operation of up to 2GHz and can run multiple programs smoothly and handle multi-threaded tasks perfectly. Pre-install Android 12 OS with Google Mobile Service support, which can be easily operated by both kids and all age groups. In addition, 500 gram lightweight design making it comfortable to hold and easy to carry on the go.,?Multifunctional hardware & ports Support?This gaming tablet 10 inch build-in a clear 5MP front cam and a 8MP rear camera, Bluetooth 5.0, dual-band Wi-Fi(2.4G/5G), dual speakers, a Type-C interface (fast charger included), a Micro TF slot, and 3.5mm headphone jack. Bring you a full range of audio-visual experience and meet the need in different usage scenarios.,?Long Battery Life? Providing a 6000mWh rechargeable battery, the power-efficient google tablet is designed to last for up to 5-7 hours on one charge (according to different scenarios) and easily charge via the Type-C port and rest assured the battery will last, so that maximize your usage needs on the move.

name: 2024 Tablet 10.1 Inch 2 in 1 Android Tablet with keyboard Octa-Core Processor 128GB Storage 1TB Expandable, 13+8MP Dual Camera, Newest Tablets PC with Case Mouse Stylus Support 5G WiFi, IPS FHD Screen
feature_bullets: ?Enjoy The Ultimate Smoothness?? TOOTON 2024 Newly Released Android tablet 10.1 inch, equipped with Unisoc T610 octa-core processor, including two 1.8Ghz A75 and six 1.8Ghz A55 processors, greatly improving the processing speed. The high performance tablet allows you to be responsive whether it's for video, music, work, e-books or multitasking.,?Larger Internal 128GB Memory?? Android 12 tablet with 4GB RAM and 128GB internal storage can download all the apps you need like Netflix, Facebook, ZOOM and etc from pre-installed Google playstore to make downloading even easier. This tablet comes with TF Card slot, it supports 4GB-1TB TF Card to give you more space to store your photos, novels, videos and various files.,?Provide Better Viewing Experience?: 2024 Tablet 10.1 inch has a wider HD screen, IPS HD screen provides better light and shadow effect for the tablet, 1280x800 resolution and Dual speakers to enjoy a clearer display.Tablet comes with reading mode can effectively protect your eyes, more suitable for long time watching and reading.,?Stay Well Connected All The Time?? 2 in 1 tablet support IEEE 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, Dual band Wifi tablet can easily connect with 5Ghz or 2.4Ghz Wifi. You don't have to worry about not being able to connect to wifi in public or at home because 2.4Ghz wifi is bursting at the seams, it's better for more scenarios, and the strong reception signal keeps you well connected all the time.,?Upgraded Long-Lasting Battery Life?? Tablet Android with 7000mAh long continuous upgrade large battery, with USB-C charging port, giving users longer entertainment and work time and shorter charging time, 10 inch tablet with parental control function can better plan the use of children's time, not excessive play tablet.,?Best Value with multiple accessories?? Tablet with keyboard (Bluetooth), wireless mouse, foldable case, stylus, charger and USB-C cable. This android tablet 10.1 inch can be used as a laptop or use as a traditional tablet. The tablet includes all the accessories you need, easy package save much.,?Wonderful Gifts?One year Warranty?? TOOTON Android tablet with elegant design and metal body is a perfect choice for Christmas, and birthday gifts. We offer a one-year manufacturer's warranty and permanent customer service. If you have any questions about the tablet, please feel free to contact our customer service.

A 5000mAh large-capacity battery can last 12 hours for general usage and standby for up to 10 days.,??Fashionable and Portable Tablet with Case?The all-metal body design of this Android tablet is stylish, lightweight, and high-end. name: Contixo Kids Tablet K103A - Tablet for Kids Toddler with 80 Disney Edition Pre-Installed, 10 inch, Android 13, 4GB, 64GB, Learning Tablet for Children, Kid-Proof Case with Kickstand (Pink)
feature_bullets: TOP RATED DISNEY APPROVED KIDS TABLET - Save up to $350.00, with 80 Disney edition APPs (Pre-installed). The exclusively featured content gives kids in 3~12 ages, including beloved classics like "Mickey's Christmas Carol," "Cars 3," "Beauty and the Beast," You also get full access to Google services and can easily download any app from the Play Store.,30% FASTER IN 2023 - Contixo kids tablet is equipped with 1.6GHz octa-core processor, Android 13 operating system, 10 inch 1280x800 IPS HD display, 4GB RAM and 64GB ROM. Our android tablet is designed to provide a safe environment to learning and entertainment. More storage for downloading favorite content.,EASY PARENTAL CONTROLS & FULL ACCESS TO GOOGLE - Kids Place allows you to control screen time and kid friendly contents. Filter feature can ensure your kids see filtered websites, apps, video channels etc. This app has no ads and no in-app purchases without your permission. You have full access to the latest Google Service such as Gmail, YouTube Kids, Netflix and many more apps and contents.,A PERFECT WiFi ANDROID TABLET FOR ONLINE LEARNING - Contixo K103 kids tablet features WiFi connectivity and full range of Google Services. Come with Google Kids Space and Youtube Kids APP, You also can download massive educational Apps from the Google Play Store such as Khan Academy for Kids, Duolingo, ABC Mouse, etc. An ultimate learning academy partner for every home.,KID-PROOF CASE & DISNEY CARTOON STICKER - The silicone case is designed to prevent the kids tablet from damage during falls and collisions. The adjustable stand on the back of the case allows toddlers to study, watch or play games. It also come with 20 Disney sticker, dress up your unique kids tablet.It's the perfect gift for your child's birthday, Christmas, or New Year's celebrations.

feature_bullets: Latest Android 13 Tablet: The tablet comes with Android 13 operating system and provides access to Google services and apps, smooth web browsing and video playback. Android 13 also prioritizes privacy and security by designing advanced app permissions that give users complete management control.,Larger Space and Smoother experience: This Android tablet runs on 1.6GHz quad-core processor and 6 (2+4) GB RAM, 64 GB internal storage and is expandable up to 128 GB via microSD (microSD not included). You can take photos and videos to capture some unforgettable moments. We have a professional and fast customer service team for technical support or return and exchange service. Included in delivery: 10 inch tablet, USB type C cable, power adapter, user manual.

name: HiGrace Kids Tablet 7 inch Android 12 Children's Tablet, Quad-Core Tablet for Kids with Parental Control, 2GB RAM+32GB ROM, Toddler Tablet with Shockproof Case, Bluetooth, Dual Camera(Pink)
feature_bullets: ?Powerful Performance?Kids Tablet 7 Inch equipped with the latest Android 12 operating system and a powerful quad-core processor, which makes apps run smoother. 2GB RAM, 32GB ROM, expandable up to 128GB, can store more videos, photos and music for your kids.,?Parental Control Mode ? Kids tablet with parental control function, which let parents to set separate profiles for each kid, add or block apps, filter contents, control screen time, and ensure they are browsing safe websites. These security settings can be adjusted as kids grow with content tailored to their age. Appropriate Age Grade Over 3 years old kids.,?Tablet with Safety Eye Protection Screen? The 7 inch kids tablet is designed with low blue light technology, equipt with a good quality 1024x600 IPS HD display screen,clear bright screen provides outstanding visual experience,plus the screen's automatic brightness adjustment,which can better protect children's eyes.,?Learning And Growing In Pleasure?Our kids tablet is perfect for entertainment and online learning. It comes preloaded with kid-friendly applications featuring the latest educational content, including games, videos, e-books, drawing, puzzles, creative arts etc. These contents can stimulate kids' imagination, creativity and self-confidence. With our tablet kids will immersed in the ocean of knowledge safely and give parents a peace of mind.,?Ideal Gift For Kids?: The upgraded child tablet for kids is designed specially for kids ages 3 and up. It is an ideal gift for your child's birthday, Children's Day, Christmas and other important holidays. Our kids tablet supports 90 days money back, 1 year warranty and life-time customer service. If you have any problems, please feel free to tell us, we will reply and solve it within 24 hours.

name: 2023 Newest 10 Inch Tablet,2 in 1 Tablet with Keyboard Mouse, Android Tablet 4G Cellular with 2 SIM 1 SD-64GB ROM SD Max 512GB,Octa-Core,1080 FHD,13MP,GMS-Zertifizierung,GPS/ WIFI/ Bluetooth(Silvery)
feature_bullets: ??[4GB+64GB+128-512GB expansion + Google GMS] ANTEMPER 2023 latest tablet 4GB+64GB, expandable up to 128-512GB. Google's GMS certified tablet is equipped with the latest version of Android, providing a personalised and secure system experience. Not only can you enjoy stable and smooth Google services, but you can also install your favourite third-party apps like YouTube, Facebook, Netflix, Prime Video and more.,??[4G LTE + 2.4G WLAN] The 10-inch tablet has dual SIM slots and supports 4G LTE network so you can work and live unhindered. Simultaneous calls and LTE networks are supported. The 2.4G WLAN allows you to stay connected to the internet wherever you are. You can switch between networks to ensure you are always connected. The Android tablet supports GPS, which enables accurate positioning.,?[8-core 1.6GHz high-performance processor + 6000mAh long-life battery]. The Unisoc chip is equipped with an Octa-Core Cortex A55 with 1.6 GHz and 8 cores. It reduces heat while giving you excellent performance. With a 6000mAh battery with large capacity, high performance and low power consumption, the tablet lasts up to 10 hours or more, so you can enjoy movies, TV shows and music for long periods of time. Type-C fast charging is supported.,??[10-inch HD screen + 13MP pixel camera] The FEONAL tablet features a 10.1-inch HD screen. The screen features G+G technology, which integrates the touch sensor into the existing structure of the LCD screen for a thinner, lighter and more responsive touch that comes to life in every moment. The rear camera features a circular stacked camera with 13 MP pixels to capture precious moments in life at any time.,??[2 Speakers + Fine Design] To give you a better external listening experience, the FEONAL Tablet With Keyboard is equipped with 2 speakers that accurately reproduce every detail of audio playback for clear sound. The Android tablet features an 8mm thick, all-metal design with rounded edges and a smooth frosting process for a soft feel and premium look. Weighing just 525 grams, it is easy to use at home or on the go.,??[Customer Support + Rich Package Contents] FEONAL is a powerful brand team that offers products with warranty and lifetime service. If you have any problems, please contact FEONAL and we will help you solve them within 24 hours. FEONAL can help with life's encounters! What's special about it is that our package also includes a keyboard, mouse and capacitive stylus, making the tablet a 2-in-1 tablet.

name: ALLDOCUBE 8.4 inch Tablet, Helio G99 Android Tablet with Widevine L1 iPlay50 Mini Pro NFE, FHD+ 1920×1200 Android13 Tablet, 16GB(8+8) RAM 256GB ROM 512GB Expandable, 5MP/13MP 4G LTE Bluetooth 5.2
feature_bullets: ????Ehanced Visual Experience???? mmerse yourself in a vibrant world of entertainment with the 8.4 inch gaming tablet. Every detail comes to life with 1920x1200 FHD resolution and In-Cell technology. WidevineL1 support ensures high-quality streaming, while 320 nit brightness and sharp contrast add depth to your visuals.,?? ?Powerful Performance??? Equipped with the MTK Helio G99 chip and Mali G57 MC2 graphics, the iPlay 50 Mini Pro NFE tablet Android guarantees smooth and lag-free gaming. Powered by Android 13 and GMS certified, you can easily download and enjoy a wide range of apps from the Google Play Store. (?? Note: While the tablet has a single speaker, we recommend using headphones or external speakers for optimal audio quality).,?? ?Ample Storage Capacity??? Never worry about running out of space again. The tablet offers 16GB RAM (8+8 virtual memory) and 256GB ROM, expandable up to 512GB with an SD card. The UFS 2.1 storage ensures fast data access and seamless file transfers, eliminating any delays.,?? ?Stay Connected, Anywhere??? The iPlay 50 Mini Pro NFE tablet keeps you connected no matter where you are. With 4G LTE, GPS, 2.4/5GHZ Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth 5.2, you can enjoy fast and stable connections. The wireless projection feature allows for seamless screen sharing, making it convenient for presentations and multimedia experiences. Additionally, the 5MP front-facing camera and 13MP rear camera can be used for capturing stunning photos, video conferencing, or attending online classes.,???Long-lasting Battery and Convenience??? The tablet is equipped with a 5000mAh battery, providing extended usage time. It supports PD 18W fast charging for quick recharge. With support for GPS, BeiDou, Galileo, and GLONASS navigation systems, it's your perfect companion for travel. Enjoy peace of mind with a one-year warranty. (?? Note: The included charger is 5V/2A, but a PD 18W charger is recommended).,Experience the ultimate in entertainment, performance, and convenience with the iPlay 50 Mini Pro NFE Android tablet. Elevate your digital experience today!

With 2.4GHz wifi function, you can enjoy many online videos or online studies at home.,?Large Battery 5000mAh ?10 inch Android tablet with 5000mAh large battery can easily work or play! The maximum charging current of tablet is 5V/2A. The package has a charger to provide you with uninterrupted work efficiency anytime, anywhere.
